<br>
I have 3 Eldrig kills.  The easy way is to have a Bard highsun the PH so you can start the cycle.  Finding the PH is the hard part, after that it is just a matter of killing lots of stuff so you don't get board waiting for the 13 min timer.<br>
<br>
One of my Eldrig kills was over at the BW zoneline... he DOES path over there and then stays in that area.  So make sure you check out that part of the zone before you set up camp.<br>
<br>
I have only seen him spawn at the 500, -4000 loc. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=146742>Tenter OneDrum</a><BR>
