<br>
I ask this because I seen Mature Chronodracs spawn (not at the specific loc) right in front of us, maybe about 500 yards off the loc mentioned above. This leads me t believe that maybe Eldrig the Old has mutiple spawn points.<br>
<br>
I just dont like waisting my guildmates time tracing down this mob. I want to get in there, complete the deed and move on!<br>
