i found this out by having a mage friend sit at the location listed and i then proceeded to go highsun everything around the wiz portal area. after about 15 min the mage reported that a mob just pathed over him but it didnt actualy spawn there. he killed the mob but i continued to high sun mobs. about 5 min later he told me one just popped on top of him and he killed it. i ran back to the spawn spot and faded to clear my agro, then i settled in for the camp with my friend.<br>
<br>
after about 20 min that mob who wandered by earlier showed up again so we killed it because it agro'd on us then the PH popped on top of us within 5 min after killing the wanderer. the next wandering mob i specifically was waiting for it to see exactly where it came from. suddenly i seen it coming from just over the hill near the cleric epic dragon ball and to my surpize it was Eldrig. my mage friend and i quickly desimated Eldrig and i was mid-looting the gut and answering tells from all my guild friends congratulating me on my epic peice when suddenly Eldrig spawned again right on top of us at the loc listed on EQdiva.<br>
<br>
my mage friend looted the gut and later MQ'd it for a guildy. just have patients and a friend to watch the spawn for you when you start highsunnin and youll knock out ELdrig in no time. <p>Elfise Pressleaf<br>
